nhc_headline: ...CENTER OF GABRIELLE CONTINUES MOVING AWAY FROM THE AZORES... ...THIS IS THE FINAL NHC ADVISORY...
summary: ...CENTER OF GABRIELLE CONTINUES MOVING AWAY FROM THE AZORES... ...THIS IS THE FINAL NHC ADVISORY... As of 3:00 PM GMT Fri Sep 26 the center of Gabrielle was located near 40.0, -22.8 with movement ENE at 31 mph. The minimum central pressure was 992 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
